room_title: Escape room "Death and Breakfast" by Adventure Vault in Miami
room_address: 3350 NW 2nd Ave Suite A4, Boca Raton, FL 33431
room_description: During a road trip with your friends, you see a thunderstorm approaching, and you decide to take refuge in a nearby bed and breakfast. You wake up in the middle of the night, and you realize you are not in your room anymore but in a dungeon! It turns out your host is a cannibal! Can you escape before you become breakfast?
